01:00:00,000 --> 01:00:03,000
<b>I am village headman Mthesewe.</b>

2
01:00:03,000 --> 01:00:11,666
<b>There are five villages that fetch water at this river.</b>

3
01:00:11,666 --> 01:00:17,541
<b>When this river dries up then things become very hard.</b>

4
01:00:17,541 --> 01:00:22,416
<b>We are looking for well wishers to support us, so that we</b>
<b>can be drinking safe water here.</b>

5
01:00:22,416 --> 01:00:29,125
<b>As it is we are drinking together with dogs and pigs.</b>

6
01:00:29,125 --> 01:00:39,500
<b>This is why we are looking for wellwishers to help us to </b>
<b>have clean and safe water. Thank you</b>
